### Health checks
GET http://localhost:8081/health

### List products with dynamic prices
GET http://localhost:8081/products

### Get product
GET http://localhost:8081/products/1

### Send user event
POST http://localhost:8082/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "u-123",
  "event": "view_product",
  "product_id": "1",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-14T10:10:00Z"
}

### Query current price
GET http://localhost:8083/price/1
